332
00:28:26,100 --> 00:28:26,940
Never mind.

333
00:28:29,300 --> 00:28:30,710
Forget this deal.

334
00:28:34,320 --> 00:28:35,180
Unless you go back

335
00:28:35,200 --> 00:28:36,710
