404
00:34:03,020 --> 00:34:04,150
I'm Duan Xu.

405
00:34:05,870 --> 00:34:07,630
My grandfather was a famous scholar.

406
00:34:09,830 --> 00:34:10,790
When I was born,

407
00:34:11,830 --> 00:34:13,580
