439
00:35:20,430 --> 00:35:21,500
I joined the All-Knowing.

440
00:35:26,790 --> 00:35:27,830
I am Duan Xu,

441
00:35:28,870 --> 00:35:29,750
Duan Shunxi.

442
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:32,470
I've never lied to you.

443
00:35:34,540 --> 00:35:35,540
See?

444
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:39,270
